{"msg":{"list":[{"title":null,"userName":"Lasia","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-18","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/wbKdib81ny6icIK0BaTrZAQPZjdCpPKAMDUgWoXUvkVcsqzWKUUicQdLDqSSXIAzKphVGZMibQL8RZHItR7wlTetH47SYQgiasgxu/0","content":"<p>两个月前，和我爸产生过一次矛盾。</p><p>我当时换了新手机，他知道后，怪我花了太多钱买手机，不懂得节省。便说，让我给家里多打些钱，正巧他们要借钱给我舅舅家盖房子。我为此很不高兴，告诉他：“你们自己的亲戚，不要找我这小辈借钱，我也没钱。” 总之，闹得很不开心。</p><p>那天晚上我爸喝酒有点醉了，又和我打电话。我突然觉得自己当时情绪太激动，说话有点重了，担心他心里也不舒服。后来跟我妈讲这件事，她说，毕竟我到了该结婚的年纪，我爸他并不是真的想要拿我的钱，而是想让我节省些，自己存点钱。</p><p>如果重来一次，</p><p>1. <span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">首先，</span>我应该克制下自己激动的情绪，联系一下之前针对我个人消费问题，我妈和我爸对此的看法，如有必要，可以和我妈啰嗦啰嗦，听我妈安慰安慰也就能冷静的思考我爸那样说的真实意义了。</p><p>2. 之后，我应该在一个冷静的时刻和我爸再次通话，告诉他我买这个手机的背景、原因、我个人消费水平、个人储蓄情况等，让他知道我这是必要的合理消费，并不影响我的储蓄行为。</p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7941,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492498323000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"球状闪电","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-18","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ajNVdqHZLLCPB8632Nxuia6CTs7I9LbKdkG6NPFtfP9L6Fr0dibaM7qSNgmGkpnL2Ac6YEAnVmEsBzHAbu4IicjuQ/0","content":"矛盾：我和妈妈因为怎么和奶奶相处，产生矛盾。<div>1.背景：妈妈觉得爷爷奶奶偏心伯伯，我试图协调，但可能语气不合适，让妈妈以为我在指责她。</div><div>2.目的：让妈妈和爷爷奶奶和睦相处。</div><div>3.相关方：妈妈、爷爷奶奶、爸爸，我和姐姐、伯伯伯母。</div><div>4.时间节点：五一奶奶生日之前。</div><div>5.可用资源：伯伯奶奶以前的举动、姐姐的沟通。</div><div>6.预期效果：妈妈能够理解老一辈人的观念，也能看到自己行为中的一些不合适的言语、举动。</div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7916,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492471208000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"张梦路","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-17","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6ZaLoY2RXU5FZibDrTsS1osmryDqKeuAvlF9licJ4nKDicnJ1HjwXTbvxdlVJj5oBJgqhR72iaGMxLcib1jJGsyWnUnj/0","content":"<p>背景：与母亲吵架，她责怪我不尊重她，责怪我不会做事。</p><p>原因：生活压力大，妈妈固执的性格。她最近更年期、脾气暴躁、全家人都很不开心。</p><p>自我感觉：经过这几次争吵，我很害怕她。她戳中了我的软肋，在我心中她不再是爱我体谅我的妈妈而是尖刀，<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px;\">我很害怕她，提到她我就想哭。</span></p><p><span style=\"line-height: 28px; background-color: transparent;\">理解偏差：</span></p><p><span style=\"line-height: 28px; background-color: transparent;\">她缺少自己的生活，日复一日围着家庭转，而家庭没有给她认同和赞美。她认为没有人理解她重视她。</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">我关注她带给我的言语伤害，认为她的诉求是无理取闹，理解不了她为什么<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">不能</span>自我改变。<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px;\">我很害怕，不能正视妈妈也是弱者和受害者，不能关注她的需求。</span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px;\">解决办法：</span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px;\">外力帮助，请心理医生或者妈妈的朋友调节。请妈妈旅游，换个生活环境。</span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px;\">改善经济条件，帮妈妈放下负担，不为生计担忧。</span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px;\">如果当面交流困难，就写信，告诉自己的状态和想法。让她放心。</span></span></span></p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7898,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492436628000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Leo","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-17","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XpSLeBeWNiaSic0ds8BMCibGZ2OUAZx2wvLS7l0JfCujUnFH561QnYtbqvZs2sAcicsmYHVHeJSgYia20o2R8WfC0mn/0","content":"<p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">家庭的距离上次太遥远了，完全想不起，还是说个同事间的吧。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">我在安排活动人员负责到各个项目的时候，出现了理解偏差，导致活动筹备阶段的效率低下，反思后发现是职责不够清晰导致的，所以重来一次的话，我会给出一个清晰的模板，包括：</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">背景——这个活动的出发点，经历了什么变化，有什么观点</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">目的——在企业层面和客户层面，黄金圈里的WHY，为什么做这个活动</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">面向客户——我们要面向的是谁，我们需要他们配合什么</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">时间节点——在哪个时间前完成哪件事</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">可用资源——是独立完成还是团队完成，有什么物资可以用</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">最后要达到什么效果——达到满分的标准，可以衡量的数据</span></p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7825,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492397690000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"潇洒鳕鱼","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-16","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98UyLlHC2Q1gMdxzMwDhQicAb4RP8PgibVuS6OEZoCGk0aIWo8mMahY8wu6ic8YFFqdsInJgJAaxbe58CIgsSXQC94U/0","content":"<p>其实出现理解偏差的时候都挺多的，这里举一个跟自己小伙伴出现的一次产生矛盾的事情：</p><p>记得有一天我上班，收到小伙伴的微信消息，说”今天由于一些原因， 工作临时不需要做了，休假一天，我去兄弟那玩会儿。“于是我就跟他回了一条”那我下班之后我们一起回家“。没想到就这样，我俩后来就产生一点矛盾，事情是这样：下班之后，我一看他没有到我公司来，我就很生气地打电话，问他”为什么没有来公司接我，我们一起从中央公园回家。“他回答说”我以为你直接坐公司交通车到我兄弟这儿来，然后我们再一起从双湖路回去啊。“</p><p>事情到了这里，从反思理解偏差的角度来看，其实就是又好气又好笑了。因为确实我们回家有两条路可以选择的，如果我当时直接再多讲一些信息，比如说”那我下班之后我们一起从中央公司这边回家“，以此消除这种理解上的误差，就不会出现上述的误会了。</p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7780,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492299949000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Echo","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-13","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4Ay0b57ibH6T3V3jNd7HDHXPdJagbpJpZ0oYN9srsbXbOyiaZS0Cqia5uToJn7saia4Gpsd3G2eB7siaedh/0","content":"我说这个是希望早点结束你们之间的讨论，并没有其他意思。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7648,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492074918000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"放开那个小Joy","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-11","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XjoaHgicBwkEqUiaGZPHI2ga7E0gShutjcib8GKdDjQktSAdYIKa4icV4VOImzSz7BGe9nzia5iaxFMrTH0qEmSRDnhN/0","content":"&nbsp;","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7509,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491880011000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"文","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-11","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XjoaHgicBwkEuUJBibwaegwqwa7rXILx7WPapDW7tTnawmINtpCLZRonooMm0ezL1xuuMLrs1trOmgp0gmOpYOuk/0","content":"<p>好像并没有发生过呢</p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7505,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491878023000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"敏","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-10","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4Ay36u84xJJa5xZVbSorVQsjiaRtdKff23d2pibDW0oSbVW3r0CUiaQtIg47Itf131L8acNXmLucqib4ibt/0","content":"<p>老公：你水壶的水不能一次性倒满吗？</p><p>我：我装很满了呀。</p><p>老公：你只装到水位线的一半。</p><p>我：但我装水时看是满的了。</p><p>老公：你过来装给我看看。</p><p>原来我装水时，手斜了，所以看到水位是到了高位，其实还差很多。</p><p>澄清误会，还是先澄清概念，看看双方认识是否一致再讨论下一步。</p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7457,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491800333000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"彭兄","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-08","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XrFctaWMO6Hek8JfFDOtEWYnA1pDX3hqjFlmjKDCFj3jID1iaMsXedtNka7iaBAcWnQiaZCCzKlMFyQ/0","content":"<p>冲突场景：老婆要我督促儿子写作业，因为没在作业上批改和签名，<span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">第二天儿子交作业被老师批评了，老婆就批评我管教儿子不上心。</span></p><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">澄清理解偏差：督促儿子写作业，包括：1、背景：大多情况下都是老婆管教，而我缺乏经验；2、目的：儿子按照老师要求（包括家长批改签名）写完作业；3、展示对象：老师；4、可用资源：儿子之前的作业、老婆的经验、家长微信群等；5、时限：当晚完成。</span></p><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">下次再有类似问题，要及时问清楚时限、目的、展示细节、可用信息资源等。</span></p><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">（写成了自我检讨也是醉了）</span></p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7399,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491637812000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"施伟","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-08","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XjoaHgicBwkEo9P2jC2S2gtzmiaPWycP2Fd6c8Lvunc8sP0iapaIrzxCur3tMr7Bia6kYfGXE4Pn3CLxmAUW8nr6ZK/0","content":"家庭的矛盾都是鸡毛蒜皮的小事！老婆是一个爱指挥干这个，干这个的人，一回到家里，你一会把水果洗了！洗完水果把孩子衣服洗了吗？任务一个接一个安排你干，她没有意识到老公一天工作很辛苦，也很疲惫，也要休息一下，也有一些自己公司的事情要在家处理，我会跟她沟通我今天工作很累，公司还有一些事情要处理一下，老婆你也挺辛苦的，这些事情你自己处理一下吧！过阵子我还会为你效劳的，谢谢老婆！改掉我自己不是好气，我没时间摆弄你，这种不好的语气和表现。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7379,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491616938000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Atia文晨","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-07","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ajNVdqHZLLB0Y2Nsibnz5eWwDJAOhMbEEbKMjQn9X8mj3icwQXoEP4xzmw1h85Miba2YMmcKSv42eFNTGXI0icWtfA/0","content":"我和我妈说你多读读书，我的意思是让我妈多读一些书好开阔眼界，让她能更加理解我.<div>而我妈误以为我嫌弃她，觉得她不够有文化（虽然她挺有文化的(･_･;）</div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7374,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491575916000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"博学笃志","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-04","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/hglMZuicA3iauTIlciaKXMtjGcyXgjKvljRv5hsGdS0pUiaecGsLTmju6ib8JdHpQwqZqXeovGLB8HRWVxBjq0BaZpicsLFdj3dfibia/0","content":"<p>关于孩子学乐器的事情，孩他爹不赞成，认为没必要，没用处。而我不屑解释。</p><p>如果重来一次，我会解释，孩子现在学习压力不是很大，学点喜欢的东西对他的成长是很有好处的。</p><p>1、孩子学习乐器，是他自己愿意的，而非强迫。<span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\">因为他非常喜欢唱歌，他希望自己能一边伴奏一边唱自己喜欢的歌。</span></p><p>2、学习乐器能够提高孩子的注意力。李笑来老师说他通过学习吉他，提高了自己的注意力。</p><p>3、学习乐器能帮助孩子培养自己的兴趣爱好。疏解孩子在学习和生活中遇到的压力和不快。</p><p><span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\">4、</span><span style=\"line-height: 25.6000003814697px; background-color: transparent;\">学习乐器还有利于</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\">锻炼耐力和毅力。让孩子感受到进步的喜悦和遭遇挫折的失意。</span></p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7191,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491305404000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"慢慢","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-01","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ajNVdqHZLLCibt7FJPfX3NmQXJgwib4vSzH4KZYdazV7mVIb2T19rMp17IOWPFRtUtw3EGtywx9BBGozp9Lacl6w/0","content":"<p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; margin-top: 0px !important;\">寒假回家的时候，家里书柜里很多弟弟以前上高中的时候用的参考书，用不上还占很多地方，然后就鼓励我弟弟把书都给扔了，我弟被我忽悠得挺开心，我们开开心心就一起挑哪些书该扔，后来扔到一半，和弟弟吵起来了，虽然最后还是把书给扔了，但是我们有半天的时间没理对方，宝贵的过年7天，就用了半天生气，觉得还是应该分析一下怎样去处理冲突，消除不必要的误会，大家和睦相处。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">目的：腾出书柜，在家里不保留用不上的东西，最重要的是我做这些只是希望弟弟、家里的状态会更好，但是当时起冲突的时候，是忽略了这个最重要的目的的</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">相关方：我、弟弟</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">背景：弟弟已经大三，高中的参考书一年年地在更新，不仅他用不上，他的这些经验也很难再通过他认为有价值的参考书传给别人</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">时间：2小时内整理完</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">资源：我们互相的理解沟通能力&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">效果/期望：<span style=\"line-height: 25.6px;\">扔掉没用的东西，才能有崭新的开始，东西不仅是对空间的占用，也是对记忆的一种占用，有空间去放新的东西，才不会被旧的东西旧的记忆纠缠，人和物总是相互关联着得。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 25.6px;\">如果能再重来，我一定不会强迫我弟弟把他所有的书都扔掉，不会去试图说服他哪怕留着也是永远都用不上的，我会帮他把他愿意扔的书扔掉，让他自己去体会扔完东西，做完决断之后的那种轻松的感觉。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 25.6px;\">我会把我的想法，我的期望全都告诉他，让他自己去做判断，而不是只是告诉他，那些书是用不上的，让他认为我只是觉得他的东西是多余的。这么一看，充分的交流真的是很有必要的。</span></p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7008,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491049691000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"晓露sheri","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-31","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4AyxPrKibibicpRzMx57Dib8I3mv4PIzcBzYNV8PZ3rMsjPExB3icliaYpuJL3KGBMEdqaAEPKN83ayRcnibO/0","content":"其实情绪上来，很难澄清，所以得首先解决情绪问题。如果家习惯性唠叨，也比较难解决\uD83D\uDE04","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7027,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1490967727000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"小鱼","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-31","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4Ay8hWCY4rsU5ic7YX8NSbKTQ1jqib9icr5cJBexUUicYhHibyRcicc1Y9Hxmc5hFqdxgaUNjiaBH4HIahUdE/0","content":"宝宝6个月后要补铁，于是开始给宝宝吃含铁米粉做辅食，我因为上班都是宝宝奶奶在喂，吃了3天我说明天给宝宝加点红薯糊糊吃。第二天宝宝奶奶就给宝宝吃的红薯糊糊，没吃米粉，其实我想说的是红薯和米粉同时吃，因为每天都要吃米粉补铁，但因为我没有说清楚，导致宝宝奶奶理解成了别的意思。如果重来，我会说：“米粉补铁，宝宝现阶段每天都要吃，另外宝宝该开始尝试新食物了，明天给宝宝吃一平勺的米粉后，再吃三分之一小碗红薯糊糊。”这样应该会更清楚吧。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":6008,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1490942696000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"零五七","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-29","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcLrFd5bPVEw4BRmkPkP5sMhsygdDwvgHiaWISQXnIXqBeHRX9uOIiciaRwETN4FxUeO0ktPBBBORFgmC37DFAUkJd0/0","content":"就搬家回原来的房子要不要粉刷墙壁一事，我和孩子的爸爸产生了分歧。我的意见是，要粉刷。孩子爸爸意见是不要粉刷。\n后来两个人平心静气的沟通了一下。\n我要粉刷的理由是，除了美观外，粉刷有一定的清洁作用。没必要在这方面省钱。\n孩子爸爸的理由是，粉刷会带来装修气味和家庭环保问题。尤其是甲醛对小孩子的伤害很大。没必要为了好看就去做一些伤害健康的事情。\n后来两人交流过后发现原来自己以为对方的理由都不是对方的真正理由。\n综合各方面因素决定还是粉刷，但是要延后搬家日期，选用比较环保的乳胶漆，尽量通风。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":6372,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1490762030000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"浅紫","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-28","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4Ay5Qias5Y6BOJq0bibrmkolNJFtbyicK1y9rN41JY4SIw04awshr8lhByygakZc9SVzOfPej1XNTbShq/0","content":"上次发生家庭矛盾是很久之前，大概是两年前，具体什么时间，什么内容，都不记得了，没有和家人住一起，没有矛盾","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":6415,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1490714975000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"张YY","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-27","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ajNVdqHZLLDC88nCjl5mticEwn6d95CyLS2K9XiaEIPB6n8icXpxKiaNZlVIVbTBj7XJVOQvkuoOHDzbycbc5YU9tA/0","content":"上一次与家人产生矛盾主要由于我找的男朋友家里不同意。\n\n如果重来一次，我询问父母，他们理想中我的男朋友是什么样的。然后，阐述我的找男朋友的标准。\n\n这样做过之后，发现我们最终的目的是相同的：就是希望我能幸福。但是对物质条件和男朋友的外貌要求存在差异。\n\n对于这些差异，通过找父母的朋友和我的朋友，用第三方的劝说，逐渐改变父母的固有的想法，最终使得我们双方能过相互理解。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":5906,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1490601775000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"王佳","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-23","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4AywoaJCYTv4hicL3wib7fApyhLPNJiaroIhefibZ5St8K9AWkmRhDQ3astuE22Q5cDMLXKe5anwROuryia/0","content":"将去澳洲的决定告诉妈妈之后，她变得很激动，我当时无法理解，和她大吵一架，说出了类似她是个不合格的母亲之类的话，以至她好几天都失眠。\n如果重来一次，我会这么做：\n1.向她表达清楚去澳洲的时间（半年后）、目的、已经准备的事情以及到澳洲后的计划，询问她的意见。\n2.澄清她的意见，是不想我离开中国还是因为害怕我在澳洲生活不下去，不想让我受苦。\n3.再次强调我的计划，并保证回国。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":5247,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1490259237000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]}],"highlightList":[],"end":false},"code":200}
